{"id": 836, "genre": 1001, "title": "作为一个体面的现代人应该遵循哪些手机礼仪？", "description": "不发长语音，不发9张自拍，不在没打招呼的情况下给人打电话。", "record_count": 11990, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181345k6f8Zz2YVLtlFaUd.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-26T11:10:48Z", "options": [{"id": 54016, "content": "不要在公车上公放夜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492195}, {"id": 54017, "content": "即时通讯软件请不要发“在吗？”，有急事请打电话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118661}, {"id": 54018, "content": "不要发不转发就怎么怎么样的链接……", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450032}, {"id": 54021, "content": "不要总是呵呵好伐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492294}, {"id": 58373, "content": "在对方发信息的时候，不要凑过来一直看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515782}, {"id": 54022, "content": "饭前怎么就不能拍菜了？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163696}, {"id": 54023, "content": "一个人呆着的时候才玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481010}, {"id": 54279, "content": "注意音量，不开闪光灯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473639}, {"id": 54025, "content": "发合照能不选只有自己拍得好看的OK？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489170}, {"id": 54026, "content": "该静音的时候请静音好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464794}, {"id": 54027, "content": "与家人或朋友一起用餐时不玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492513}, {"id": 54028, "content": "看演唱会别在朋友圈连发小视频，忍着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492498}, {"id": 54029, "content": "敏感信息及时删，否则心总悬着怕她（他）翻", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491937}, {"id": 54031, "content": "微信找别人有事的时候，先打文字，不要直接发语音过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225788}, {"id": 54032, "content": "没经过同意不看他人照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311392}, {"id": 58896, "content": "一起出去玩的时候，放下手机好吗！和室友四个人出去经常看她们三个刷！手！机！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 455019}, {"id": 54033, "content": "别看伦家的相册好不啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 457935}, {"id": 54034, "content": "朋友出来聚餐，同学聚会，就应该放下手机，就连约会吃饭，也是面对面玩手机，这是个病态的社会现象", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492632}, {"id": 54291, "content": "不要因为手机忽视了爱你的他(她)！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290001}, {"id": 54036, "content": "吃饭聊天聚会不碰手机?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492634}, {"id": 54292, "content": "手机没电了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290001}, {"id": 54039, "content": "手机时时静音", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478748}, {"id": 54299, "content": "“请赞一下朋友圈第一条谢谢”（╯‵□′）╯︵┴─┴", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494216}, {"id": 54562, "content": "看电影的时候不要拍照,更不要开闪光灯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496400}, {"id": 60706, "content": "别人跟你说话的时候不要只顾着低头刷手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527580}, {"id": 54055, "content": "不在飞机上开手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223145}, {"id": 54057, "content": "公共场合唱歌小点声", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492697}, {"id": 54571, "content": "为自己言论负责", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496498}, {"id": 53550, "content": "看照片不手贱地左右滑动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1426, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 53551, "content": "饭前不拍菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 698, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 54063, "content": "不带手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488657}, {"id": 53552, "content": "不在人多拥挤的地方用自拍杆", "image": null, "praise_count": 466, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 54064, "content": "不带手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488657}, {"id": 56624, "content": "都要遵守", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507235}, {"id": 54065, "content": "不要发超过15秒的语音", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448164}, {"id": 53811, "content": "不随意试别人的手机密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 274, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470495}, {"id": 56115, "content": "呵呵 每次地铁上瞧见那些 瞥别人手机屏幕的老货 就恨不得一脚踹上去 怎么破～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504850}, {"id": 53812, "content": "不偷窥别人的手机解锁密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 901, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460896}, {"id": 54068, "content": "出去旅游一天最多发一条盆友圈", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193901EQsCv6OutoLF0lNj.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159716}, {"id": 59444, "content": "出去玩吃饭的时候麻烦不要一直看手机很不礼貌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 520718}, {"id": 53813, "content": "不在电影院把后置摄像头变成提示音闪亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 456, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377515}, {"id": 54069, "content": "不随意打量别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492917}, {"id": 53814, "content": "谨慎使用“哦”“嗯”等预期助词。", "image": null, "praise_count": 333, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490803}, {"id": 54070, "content": "相册QQ微信微博即使没有退出也不要当个好奇宝宝去看哦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489724}, {"id": 53815, "content": "和朋友一起吃饭时把手机放下，少刷一会死不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1459, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107293}, {"id": 53816, "content": "不要随手拍 不p就放到朋友圈 可能一定会撕逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 418962}, {"id": 53817, "content": "认为自己有强迫症看不惯少于九张的图", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185396}, {"id": 54073, "content": "特定场合静音，不偷看别人在干什么，好多", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492957}, {"id": 54329, "content": "摘要中两个，文字聊天聊着聊着来段长语音就很没劲了好吗，语音没听完突然又来个电话实在很扫兴耶。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495183}, {"id": 53818, "content": "一起吃饭不玩手机！！！！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 429, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458087}]}